18
00:00:12,582 --> 00:00:15,582
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:18,606 --> 00:00:21,150
<i>Supreme Chancellor in peril!</i>

20
00:00:21,234 --> 00:00:23,611
<i>After surviving the ordeals of "The Box, "</i>

21
00:00:23,653 --> 00:00:27,740
<i>Obi-Wan Kenobi, working undercover
as assassin Rako Hardeen,</i>

22
00:00:27,782 --> 00:00:31,285
<i>is invited to join Count Dooku's plot
against Chancellor Palpatine.</i>

23
00:00:31,786 --> 00:00:34,163
<i>Working with a team
of deadly bounty hunters,</i>

24
00:00:34,247 --> 00:00:36,874
<i>Obi-Wan travels to the planet of Naboo</i>

25
00:00:36,958 --> 00:00:39,794
<i>where the Chancellor
will preside over the Festival of Light.</i>

26
00:00:39,877 --> 00:00:44,257
<i>Now, as the Jedi Council and Count Dooku
finalize their respective plans,</i>

27
00:00:44,298 --> 00:00:47,301
<i>a deadly confrontation seems inevitable.</i>

28
00:00:47,802 --> 00:00:49,720
As you can see,
we've mapped the Chancellor's route

29
00:00:49,804 --> 00:00:51,472
to and from the festival stage.

30
00:00:51,556 --> 00:00:54,809
We know where he'll be at every moment
from the time we land on Naboo.

31
00:00:54,850 --> 00:00:56,936
What security measures are in place?

32
00:00:58,604 --> 00:01:00,356
The Naboo Royal Guard
will have armed sentries

33
00:01:00,439 --> 00:01:02,149
at all entry points on the palace.

34
00:01:02,191 --> 00:01:04,610
And the stage itself
will be sealed off by a ray shield

35
00:01:04,652 --> 00:01:06,153
for the duration of the event.

36
00:01:06,195 --> 00:01:08,155
I see nothing here to worry about.

37
00:01:08,197 --> 00:01:11,158
With complacency comes vulnerability.

38
00:01:11,242 --> 00:01:12,243
Yes.

39
00:01:12,493 --> 00:01:15,496
It is what we do not see that concerns me.

40
00:01:15,830 --> 00:01:19,584
A long time to plan his attack,
Count Dooku has.

41
00:01:20,167 --> 00:01:21,210
Yes.

42
00:01:21,294 --> 00:01:23,337
We thought we'd have an advantage
with Obi-Wan on the inside,

43
00:01:24,171 --> 00:01:26,632
but we've had no communication from him
in days.

44
00:01:26,674 --> 00:01:30,511
Obi-Wan will do his part.
Let's make sure we do ours.

45
00:01:48,529 --> 00:01:50,573
Whoa!

46
00:02:06,714 --> 00:02:07,840
Shh!

47
00:02:23,272 --> 00:02:24,940
Well, hello there.

48
00:02:32,657 --> 00:02:33,741
All clear!

49
00:02:44,335 --> 00:02:48,047
This is it, my friends.
The day of reckoning for the Republic.

50
00:02:48,506 --> 00:02:51,050
I have it from a very reliable source

51
00:02:51,092 --> 00:02:54,303
that everything will happen
exactly as we planned.

52
00:02:54,387 --> 00:02:56,889
Execute your roles
as you've been instructed,

53
00:02:56,931 --> 00:02:59,809
and you will all be immortalized in history.

54
00:02:59,892 --> 00:03:02,478
Not to mention,
rewarded with enough credits

55
00:03:02,561 --> 00:03:05,147
that you will never have to work again.

56
00:03:05,314 --> 00:03:08,234
I will let Cad Bane take it from here.

57
00:03:09,443 --> 00:03:11,779
Listen up, I'm only saying it once.

58
00:03:12,363 --> 00:03:15,032
Each device tells you your position

59
00:03:15,116 --> 00:03:18,285
and essential details
about your part of the plot.

60
00:03:18,828 --> 00:03:20,830
Aren't you gonna tell us
how all the pieces fit together?

61
00:03:21,497 --> 00:03:24,709
Derrown here is going to breach the shield.

62
00:03:24,792 --> 00:03:27,461
Moralo Eval is the getaway driver.

63
00:03:27,545 --> 00:03:31,090
Two of you will act as guards
protecting the Chancellor.

64
00:03:31,465 --> 00:03:34,093
And you, Hardeen,

65
00:03:36,387 --> 00:03:37,847
are a sniper.

66
00:03:39,765 --> 00:03:41,600
That's all you need to know.

67
00:03:42,017 --> 00:03:43,477
Once we have the Chancellor,

68
00:03:43,519 --> 00:03:46,689
the devices will lead you
to the rendezvous point.

69
00:03:46,772 --> 00:03:48,649
Any questions?

70
00:03:48,691 --> 00:03:51,402
Now for our disguises. Everyone step back.

71
00:03:53,529 --> 00:03:55,072
This will get us into the inner circle.

72
00:03:55,614 --> 00:03:59,827
Step into the shadow hologram
and you will receive your new identity.

73
00:04:08,836 --> 00:04:09,920
When you leave here, you will have

74
00:04:10,004 --> 00:04:12,840
no communication
with the rest of the team.

75
00:04:13,466 --> 00:04:15,885
All right, then, get to your positions.

76
00:04:17,553 --> 00:04:21,849
Well handled.
I should have put you in charge long ago.

77
00:04:21,891 --> 00:04:23,392
A word of advice, though,

78
00:04:24,185 --> 00:04:26,312
keep an eye on Hardeen.

79
00:04:26,812 --> 00:04:30,441
There's something about him I do not trust.

80
00:04:30,524 --> 00:04:33,611
Don't worry.
I'm keeping my eye on all of them.

81
00:05:10,022 --> 00:05:11,816
Greetings, Your Majesty.

82
00:05:12,191 --> 00:05:14,068
Welcome home, Chancellor.

83
00:05:14,151 --> 00:05:16,612
I'm thankful to the Jedi
for bringing you here safely.

84
00:05:17,112 --> 00:05:19,990
Yes, Senator, it is good to be back,

85
00:05:20,074 --> 00:05:25,120
although I think the amount of security
that has accompanied me is overkill.

86
00:05:25,204 --> 00:05:27,540
With all due respect, Chancellor,

87
00:05:27,581 --> 00:05:32,545
where your safety is concerned
there is no such thing as overkill.

88
00:05:32,753 --> 00:05:35,214
So you keep insisting, Master Jedi.

89
00:05:35,256 --> 00:05:37,258
But I've grown tired of discussing it.

90
00:05:39,385 --> 00:05:42,680
Anakin, Ahsoka, welcome to the festival.

91
00:05:43,138 --> 00:05:47,059
I've never seen the Festival of Light.
Sounds like a big event.

92
00:05:47,101 --> 00:05:49,103
They're expecting a large crowd,

93
00:05:49,186 --> 00:05:52,690
which means it will be difficult for Dooku
to attack during the ceremony.

94
00:05:52,773 --> 00:05:55,401
That leaves the palace
as the best opportunity for an ambush.

95
00:05:55,818 --> 00:05:58,195
Are you that certain an attack is imminent?

96
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:59,738
I'm afraid so,

97
00:05:59,780 --> 00:06:02,157
which is why I'm making Ahsoka
your personal bodyguard.

98
00:06:02,658 --> 00:06:04,952
At your service, My Lady.

99
00:06:05,035 --> 00:06:07,079
If there's trouble,
Ahsoka will get you, the Queen,

100
00:06:07,121 --> 00:06:08,956
and the rest of your staff to safety.

101
00:06:09,039 --> 00:06:10,207
What about you?

102
00:06:10,291 --> 00:06:12,793
Hopefully, I'll be where I always am.

103
00:06:12,835 --> 00:06:15,504
-He means saving the day.
-Of course he does.

104
00:06:45,993 --> 00:06:48,621
Make sure you have two guards posted.

105
00:06:48,662 --> 00:06:50,122
Excuse me.

106
00:06:51,624 --> 00:06:56,712
-Obi-Wan, thank goodness you're alive.
<i>-Yes, I've seen better days.</i>

107
00:06:56,795 --> 00:06:57,922
I'm here, in Theed.

108
00:06:59,673 --> 00:07:02,468
<i>- So Dooku's plan is still on?</i>
- Yes.

109
00:07:02,509 --> 00:07:05,012
<i>How are they planning
to attack the Chancellor?</i>

110
00:07:05,095 --> 00:07:07,806
Three of the bounty hunters
are disguised as senate guards.

111
00:07:07,848 --> 00:07:09,183
Eval is the getaway driver

112
00:07:09,224 --> 00:07:11,852
and they have a Parwan
that can pass through the ray shield.

113
00:07:11,936 --> 00:07:13,228
I have a sniper rifle.

114
00:07:13,312 --> 00:07:16,190
Don't worry. It's loaded with stun blasts.

115
00:07:16,231 --> 00:07:19,526
I'm supposed to immobilize the Chancellor,
not kill him.

116
00:07:19,610 --> 00:07:20,611
<i>Where are you?</i>

117
00:07:20,694 --> 00:07:23,322
In a tower overlooking the plaza.

118
00:07:23,364 --> 00:07:25,574
So the attack
is going to take place outside.

119
00:07:25,658 --> 00:07:28,118
<i>Yes. From here,
I can be your eye in the sky.</i>

120
00:07:28,702 --> 00:07:30,955
I'll be able to tell you
everything that's going on.

121
00:07:32,414 --> 00:07:34,333
They will try to infiltrate the security area.

122
00:07:34,375 --> 00:07:37,044
Make sure you have someone
double check the guards' identities.

123
00:07:37,127 --> 00:07:39,046
<i>That's going to take time.</i>

124
00:07:39,088 --> 00:07:42,007
<i>You'll have to do your best, my friend.</i>

125
00:08:11,245 --> 00:08:12,246
The stage is set.

126
00:08:12,579 --> 00:08:13,831
<i>Activate the ray shield.</i>

127
00:08:14,498 --> 00:08:16,166
Copy that, General Skywalker.

128
00:08:30,222 --> 00:08:33,475
It is an honor to be here
for this momentous occasion.

129
00:08:33,642 --> 00:08:37,855
The pride I feel for this planet
cannot be put into words.

130
00:08:38,397 --> 00:08:43,152
847 years ago, Naboo joined the Republic,

131
00:08:44,194 --> 00:08:47,156
and tonight we celebrate that union!

132
00:09:01,086 --> 00:09:03,172
What's
your identification number?

133
00:09:03,297 --> 00:09:05,299
SG-1984.

134
00:09:05,716 --> 00:09:08,635
All right, move along,
but stay sharp.

135
00:09:10,054 --> 00:09:14,433
Take a moment
and look around this glorious city of yours.

136
00:09:14,475 --> 00:09:18,562
It wasn't long ago
this was all plasma mines.

137
00:09:18,645 --> 00:09:21,982
Naboo has indeed come a long way.

138
00:09:22,066 --> 00:09:25,652
But as we chart
a bold course for the future,

139
00:09:25,694 --> 00:09:29,114
let us never forget our past!

140
00:09:41,251 --> 00:09:43,462
Mace, so far so good.

141
00:09:46,256 --> 00:09:47,257
Gotcha!

142
00:09:47,633 --> 00:09:50,177
East side! The security guard on the stairs.

143
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:52,596
Skywalker! The shield generator!

144
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:04,733
All right, you two,

145
00:10:04,817 --> 00:10:07,361
take the Chancellor to that speeder
and get him out of here.

146
00:10:09,029 --> 00:10:10,864
This way, Your Majesty. Hurry!

147
00:10:32,886 --> 00:10:34,388
Blast! It's only good for one shot.

148
00:10:37,015 --> 00:10:40,227
Mace, Anakin's down
and I don't see Bane anywhere.

149
00:10:41,061 --> 00:10:42,146
I'll find him.

150
00:10:43,772 --> 00:10:45,190
Let's make the switch.

151
00:11:02,875 --> 00:11:05,252
You're coming with me, Chancellor.

152
00:11:09,548 --> 00:11:12,092
Those tentacles
pack quite a punch.

153
00:11:12,176 --> 00:11:13,177
Come on.

154
00:11:14,887 --> 00:11:18,056
The Chancellor! The guard escorting them
is a bounty hunter!

155
00:11:29,401 --> 00:11:30,777
Chancellor, are you all right?

156
00:11:37,826 --> 00:11:39,328
Where is the Chancellor?

157
00:11:41,371 --> 00:11:42,789
Move it, move it!

158
00:11:50,339 --> 00:11:52,382
So long, Jedi!

159
00:12:01,266 --> 00:12:02,517
I'm going after the Chancellor.

160
00:12:02,601 --> 00:12:03,977
Copy that, Obi-Wan.

161
00:12:04,019 --> 00:12:06,980
I'll send you the coordinates
and hold Bane there as long as I can.

162
00:12:14,488 --> 00:12:18,700
This is the rendezvous point.
Dooku said he would meet us here.

163
00:12:21,328 --> 00:12:26,500
What did I tell you, Bane?
My plan worked to perfection.

164
00:12:27,793 --> 00:12:29,753
It wasn't your plan.

165
00:12:29,836 --> 00:12:32,839
It was my execution of your plan.

166
00:12:33,006 --> 00:12:34,174
Come on, get up.

167
00:12:34,258 --> 00:12:38,053
How dare you disrespect Moralo Eval!

168
00:12:38,136 --> 00:12:40,514
Pipe down. Where's Dooku?

169
00:12:40,597 --> 00:12:42,683
I thought you said he'd meet us here?

170
00:12:42,766 --> 00:12:44,434
That was the plan.

171
00:12:48,855 --> 00:12:51,358
Hardeen, you're not supposed
to be here yet.

172
00:12:51,400 --> 00:12:54,861
I don't want to be double-crossed
and left behind again.

173
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:59,199
I think we've all been double-crossed.
Dooku's a no-show.

174
00:12:59,241 --> 00:13:02,035
What do you mean?
What do we do with the Chancellor now?

175
00:13:02,619 --> 00:13:05,205
We'll ransom him ourselves.

176
00:13:05,289 --> 00:13:08,583
If Dooku won't pay us, somebody else will.

177
00:13:09,042 --> 00:13:11,753
I'm afraid the Chancellor's coming with me.

178
00:13:49,249 --> 00:13:52,711
Please! Do not kill Moralo Eval!

179
00:13:53,128 --> 00:13:55,172
Take him and Bane into custody.

180
00:13:55,255 --> 00:13:58,592
And make sure the Chancellor
is returned safely to the palace.

181
00:13:59,968 --> 00:14:02,637
You did a good job, Obi-Wan.

182
00:14:03,722 --> 00:14:07,851
Kenobi ! I should have known.

183
00:14:07,934 --> 00:14:11,730
Something smelled wrong about you
from the start.

184
00:14:11,772 --> 00:14:16,193
Yes, well, spending so much time with you
was no reward either.

185
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:21,281
Reward ! I'll give you a reward,
when I plug you full of laser bolts!

186
00:14:22,783 --> 00:14:24,701
Such a pleasant fellow.

187
00:14:24,785 --> 00:14:26,578
I hope this was all worth it.

188
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:29,915
We saved the Chancellor.
That's the important thing.

189
00:14:43,470 --> 00:14:47,516
Once again, you have all distinguished
yourselves in the eyes of the Republic.

190
00:14:47,599 --> 00:14:49,935
The people of Naboo are in your debt.

191
00:14:50,352 --> 00:14:52,312
It's all part of the job, My Lady.

192
00:14:57,818 --> 00:14:59,820
I'm not sure I agree with your orders

193
00:14:59,903 --> 00:15:02,864
to send the rest of the security detail
back to Coruscant.

194
00:15:02,948 --> 00:15:08,328
Now that the threat has passed,
I think Anakin is all the security I need.

195
00:15:09,704 --> 00:15:11,415
You look terrible.

196
00:15:12,457 --> 00:15:14,543
Being a criminal's not easy work.

197
00:15:14,626 --> 00:15:17,129
If I'd known what was going on,
I could've helped you.

198
00:15:17,170 --> 00:15:19,464
Too bad the Council didn't trust me.

199
00:15:20,549 --> 00:15:23,718
Anakin, it was my decision
to keep the truth from you.

200
00:15:24,428 --> 00:15:28,223
I knew if you were convinced I was dead,
Dooku would believe it as well.

201
00:15:28,723 --> 00:15:30,225
Your decision?

202
00:15:30,308 --> 00:15:32,602
Look, I know
I did some questionable things,

203
00:15:32,686 --> 00:15:35,021
but I did what I had to do.

204
00:15:35,063 --> 00:15:36,857
I hope you can understand that.

205
00:15:36,898 --> 00:15:38,358
You lied to me!

206
00:15:38,442 --> 00:15:41,194
How many other lies
have I been told by the Council?

207
00:15:42,279 --> 00:15:45,532
And how do you know
that you even have the whole truth?

208
00:15:57,794 --> 00:16:00,005
We should get you
into the transformation chamber.

209
00:16:00,046 --> 00:16:03,633
Everyone's a little tired
of looking at that ugly face of yours.

210
00:16:03,717 --> 00:16:06,178
This is the face that saved the Republic.

211
00:16:06,219 --> 00:16:08,054
But I think you're right.

212
00:16:08,096 --> 00:16:09,973
It's time to go back
to being Obi-Wan Kenobi.

213
00:16:10,724 --> 00:16:13,310
I can sense something is still bothering you.

214
00:16:14,436 --> 00:16:18,023
Yes, something Anakin said
has me worried.

215
00:16:18,899 --> 00:16:21,026
Do we know the whole truth?

216
00:16:22,527 --> 00:16:26,072
I think I'll stay.
I need to check one last thing.

217
00:17:05,779 --> 00:17:08,031
Dooku was listening ! He knew all along.

218
00:17:09,282 --> 00:17:12,327
We will leave as soon
as Queen Neeyutnee's banquet is over.

219
00:17:12,410 --> 00:17:15,080
I also want to say goodbye
to Senator Amidala.

220
00:17:15,121 --> 00:17:17,249
She has been a very gracious host.

221
00:17:17,457 --> 00:17:20,502
Hmm. Padmé didn't mention
a banquet to me.

222
00:17:20,919 --> 00:17:23,338
Perhaps she meant it as a surprise.

223
00:17:23,630 --> 00:17:27,968
I must say, the lengths the Jedi
will go to is nothing short of incredible.

224
00:17:28,635 --> 00:17:34,015
I assume the brilliant plan
to disguise Obi-Wan Kenobi was yours.

225
00:17:34,099 --> 00:17:37,852
No, it wasn't, sir.
I was in the dark as much as you were.

226
00:17:38,520 --> 00:17:40,605
Really? Interesting.

227
00:17:40,647 --> 00:17:44,150
I was under the impression
the Jedi always worked as a team.

228
00:17:46,027 --> 00:17:47,028
Welcome!

229
00:17:50,991 --> 00:17:52,534
My gracious, it's a trap!

230
00:17:54,077 --> 00:17:55,245
Chancellor, stay back!

231
00:17:59,833 --> 00:18:02,836
You should've quit
while you were still alive, Dooku!

232
00:18:05,422 --> 00:18:10,010
Fighting off the entire Jedi security force
would have been difficult.

233
00:18:10,093 --> 00:18:12,470
But now that they are gone,

234
00:18:13,346 --> 00:18:16,600
defeating you alone will be an easy task.

235
00:18:35,327 --> 00:18:36,786
Chancellor, get out of here!

236
00:18:38,038 --> 00:18:39,372
Good idea.

237
00:18:43,668 --> 00:18:44,669
Unhand me!

238
00:20:04,290 --> 00:20:05,458
Are you all right?

239
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,001
Come on!

240
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:32,736
Well done, Master Kenobi.
You are a worthy adversary.

241
00:20:32,819 --> 00:20:36,239
I cannot say the same
about your young apprentice.

242
00:20:43,788 --> 00:20:46,040
Chancellor, are you all right?

243
00:20:47,208 --> 00:20:50,837
Yes, thanks again to the heroics of the Jedi.

244
00:20:51,337 --> 00:20:53,423
That's the second time today.

245
00:20:53,506 --> 00:20:56,134
We specialize in heroics, Chancellor.

246
00:20:56,718 --> 00:21:00,722
As long as I live, no harm
will ever come to you, Your Excellency.

247
00:21:00,847 --> 00:21:06,102
Hmm. Well, here's to your long
and prosperous life, Anakin.

248
00:21:07,020 --> 00:21:09,522
One shudders to think
where the galaxy would be

249
00:21:09,606 --> 00:21:11,357
